致信抗疫妻子：拌嘴都会哭鼻子的小女生，怎会不害怕。
Letter to the wife of the plague: the mouth will cry the little girl, how can not be afraid.
澎湃新闻。
The news is roaring.
澎湃新闻                      。
The news is roaring.
澎湃新闻。
The news is roaring.
有内涵的时政新媒体。
Connotation of the new political media.
澎湃新闻记者 李文姬一个家庭，两位白衣天使。
Peng Pai journalist Li WenJi a family, two angels in white.
现在，他们又同是与新冠病毒厮杀的战士——妻子江兰是武汉亚心总医院神经科护士，丈夫段志钢则是南部战区空军某场站医院医生。
Now, they are also fighting the new crown virus - wife Jiang Lan is Wuhan Axin General Hospital neurology nurses, her husband Duan Zhigang is a southern theater air force station hospital doctor.
江兰给病人加油打气 南部战区空军某场站供图正月初二，江兰被科室紧急召回，负责重症和疑似病例的护理。
Jiang Lan to the patient refueling a southern theater air force station for the first two months of the first year, Jiang Lan was recalled emergency departments, responsible for severe and suspected cases of care.
神经科的一些重症患者需要做吸痰和气切护理，如果这些人患有新冠肺炎，对医护人员来讲这将是一项极度危险的操作。
Some patients with severe neurological conditions need suction and resection care, which can be extremely dangerous for health-care workers if they develop pneumonia.
江兰回去后没几天，医院陆续有病人确诊为新冠肺炎，又过了几天，她所在科室有医生倒下了。
A few days after Jiang Lan returned, the hospital was confirmed as the new crown pneumonia, and a few days later, her department had a doctor down.
段志钢问妻子：“你怕不怕？”看着丈夫紧张兮兮的样子，江兰反而笑着安慰：“不怕，这是我的本职工作，为大武汉做点我力所能及的事情。
Duan Zhigang asked his wife, "Are you afraid of it?" Looking at her husband nervously, Jiang Lan smiled and said, "No fear, this is my job to do something I can for Wuhan.
我只怕我万一中招了，会带回来给你。
I'm just afraid I'll bring it back in case I confess.
”“一个和我拌嘴都会偷偷哭鼻子的小女生，面对如此凶猛的疫情怎么会不害怕呢？”分别近一个月，段志钢把平日无法说出口的情绪写进了给爱妻的书信。
"" A little girl who spits with me will cry secretly, how can she not be afraid in the face of such a fierce outbreak? "
尽管同样在与疫情作斗争，但看着冲在一线的妻子，段志钢感到既心疼又愧疚：“一个人需要鼓足多大的勇气才敢去和死神较量？作为一名医生，一名人民子弟兵，冲在前的应该是我啊。
Even as he struggles with the epidemic, Duan Zhigang feels both hurt and guilty as he watches his wife hurtling down the line: "How much courage does a man need to muster to challenge death?
”在信的结尾，段志钢动情地写道：“不必顾虑分心，我是你坚实的臂膀，你千万注意安全，一定做好防护，我在家中等你平安归来！下次换我来守护你！”江兰穿戴防护装备，准备进入隔离区经本人同意，澎湃新闻现将此信刊载。
"Don't worry about the distraction," Duan wrote feelingly at the end of the letter. "I'm your firm arm. You must be safe. I'll wait at home for you to return safely.
江兰吾妻：见信如唔一定非常惊讶吧，朝夕相处为什么要写信，难道有什么话不能当面说吗？毕竟上一封信还是在刚恋爱时写的。
Why do you write to each other at night? After all, the last letter was written when I was in love.
是的，我的有些小情绪还是需要用书信才能表达。
Yes, I still need to use letters to express some of my small emotions.
2020年的春节注定是一个让全国人民心情都阴郁的节日，新型冠状病毒肺炎疫情来势汹汹，其传播之快、波及之广、影响之大，远远超出了我们的想象。
The 2020 Spring Festival is bound to be a sombre day for the whole nation. The new coronavirus pneumonia has become a serious threat, spreading far beyond our wildest dreams.
截至2月20日，全国已确诊病例7万余人。
As of February 20, more than 70,000 cases had been confirmed nationwide.
这场突如其来的灾难极大地破坏了人们的生活秩序，也让武汉一下子成为了举世瞩目的焦点。
This sudden disaster greatly destroyed people's life order, and let Wuhan suddenly become the focus of world attention.
你们科室有医生倒下了，所幸你复查两次肺部CT均是正常的。
Your department has a doctor down, fortunately you review two pulmonary CT is normal.
你就是这么一个人，考虑别人总会比自己多些。
You are one of those people who always think more about others than you do about yourself.
每每和我谈及单位的工作，有愤慨，有焦虑，也有感动，唯独未曾有过一丝的畏惧。
I often talk about the work of the unit, there is indignation, anxiety, also moved, but there has never been a trace of fear.
一个和我拌嘴都会偷偷哭鼻子的小女生，面对如此凶猛的疫情怎么会不害怕呢，无非是怕我和家人担心罢了！一个人需要鼓足多大的勇气才敢去和死神较量！每每想到此我既心疼又愧疚，作为一名医生，一名人民子弟兵，冲在前的应该是我啊！生命宝贵，也很脆弱，尤其是在这场没有硝烟的战争中，敌人的狡猾远远超出我们的想象。
How can a girl who quarrel with me secretly cry without fear in the face of such a ferocious outbreak of disease is nothing but fear of me and my family! How much courage must a man muster to challenge death!
当疾病在武汉城里肆虐，当祖国和人民把希望寄托在我们身上的时候，穿上了这身白大褂，我们就是一名战士，当义无反顾奋勇逆行，用尽全力追求最后的胜利，矢志不渝践行我们的医学誓言：“健康所系，性命相托。
When the disease ravages Wuhan city, when the motherland and people put their hopes on us, wearing this white coat, we are a soldier, when unswerving, with all our efforts to pursue the final victory, unswervingly practice our medical oath: "Health is in the hands of life.
我决心竭尽全力除人类之病痛，助健康之完美，维护医术的圣洁和荣誉，救死扶伤，不辞艰辛，执着追求，为祖国医药卫生事业的发展和人类身心健康奋斗终生”。
I am determined to do my utmost to remove the maladies of mankind, to help perfect health, to preserve the sanctity and honor of medicine, to save lives and wounds, to persevere in pursuit and to work hard for the development of Chinese medicine and health and the physical and mental health of mankind. "
这样，才能问心无愧，不负韶华。
In this way, can a clear conscience, meet Shaohua.
这样的人生才有意义！况且我们有党和国家这个坚强的后盾，有全国人民的八方支援，有六万武汉医疗战线的白衣战士，我们一定能战胜疫情。
Besides, with the strong backing of the Party and state, the support of the people from all over the country, and the white-clothed warriors on the Wuhan medical front, we are sure to overcome the epidemic.
不必顾虑分心，我是你坚实的臂膀，你千万注意安全，一定做好防护，我在家中等你平安归来！下次换我来守护你！爱你的老段2020年2月21日晚本期编辑 邢潭推荐阅读。
Don't worry about the distraction, I am your solid arm, you must pay attention to safety, do a good job of protection, I wait for you at home safe return! Next time change me to guard you! Love your old paragraph February 21, 2020 evening editor Xingtan read.
